{
  "texts": [
    "Dialects can have an impact on annotation itself.",
    "Farha and Magdy [2022] show that dialect familiarity helps sarcasm annotation.",
    "Mdhaffar et al. [2017] create a dataset of 17000 Facebook comments labeled with sentiment in Tunisian dialect of Arabic.",
    "Assiri et al. [2018] present a sentiment-labeled lexicon of words in the Saudi dialect of Arabic, and use simple counting-based sentiment analysis.",
    "Husain et al. [2022] use weakly supervised labels for sentiment analysis of tweets in the Kuwaiti dialect of Arabic."
  ]
}